results.name: Multix Big Kid 'Black White'
results.story: The adidas Multix Big Kid ‘Black White’ pairs an essential color palette with a versatile silhouette built for play. The upper is constructed from breathable black mesh, reinforced with tonal no-sew skins and a synthetic leather heel overlay. A contrasting white adidas tag adorns the mesh tongue, matching the signature three-stripes that decorate the sneaker’s quarter panel. An Ortholite sockliner combines with a full-length EVA midsole to deliver cushioned comfort with every step.

results.name: Force 1 Toggle PS 'Black Volt'
results.story: The Nike Force 1 Toggle PS ‘Black Volt’ enables little kids to easily slip on or off their shoes. Traditional laces are replaced by Flyease closure, comprising a toggle system and a Volt-colored hook-and-loop pull tab. Additional pops of Volt land on the sneaker’s branding elements, allowing them to stand out against a black leather backdrop. A matching black rubber cupsole, complete with the AF1’s signature pivot point traction pattern, anchors the revised low-top.

results.name: Multix Little Kid 'Black White'
results.story: The adidas Multix Little Kid ‘Black White’ highlights an essential color palette on a versatile sneaker built for everyday wear. The breathable upper is constructed from black mesh, accented with contrasting white three-stripes and fortified with tonal fused overlays. An Ortholite sockliner works in concert with a pristine EVA midsole to deliver lightweight cushioning with every step. Underfoot, a matching white rubber outsole provides grippy traction.

results.name: Air Jordan 9 Retro GS 'Dark Charcoal University Gold'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Air Jordan 9 Retro GS ‘Dark Charcoal University Gold’ presents a subdued colorway of the silhouette that released when Michael Jordan had temporarily stepped away from the game. Black and charcoal tones are applied to the nubuck upper, equipped with interior bootie construction and a speed lacing system. Contrasting hits of University Gold land on the collar lining and heel, featuring a webbing pull tab and an embroidered 23. A matching gold Jumpman adorns the PU midsole, housing an encapsulated Air unit in the heel.

Kyrie 7 GS 'Roswell Rayguns'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Kyrie 7 GS ‘Roswell Rayguns’ draws inspiration from the fictional ABA team of the same name, originally featured in a series of Nike Basketball TV ads that ran in 2002. The team’s signature hues are utilized on Kyrie Irving’s seventh signature shoe, highlighted by a layered mesh upper in black and orange. A synthetic leather heel overlay in University Gold is embellished with an embroidered Rayguns graphic, a design detail first deployed on the 2005 ‘Raygun’ Nike SB Dunk and repeated on a special-edition Kyrie 3.

results.name: Dunk Low PS 'Chinese New Year - Firecracker'
results.story: Launching as part of the brand’s Chinese New Year collection, the Nike Dunk Low PS ‘Firecracker’ delivers a celebratory colorway of the classic silhouette made for little kids. The low-top’s graphic-print overlays are inspired by colorful firecracker wrapping paper, while the mismatched tongue tags depict cautionary warning labels. The entire outer layer of the upper can be worn away to reveal a bright red finish denoting the casing of a firecracker. A third and final layer reveals a grey base with black overlays, the neutral tones representing the gun powder residue from a spent firecracker.

J. Cole x RS-Dreamer 2 Jr 'Janurary 28th'
results.story: Offered in kids sizing, the J. Cole x PUMA RS-Dreamer 2 Jr ‘January 28th’ represents the debut colorway of the rapper’s second signature basketball shoe. Named for a track from the album ‘2014 Forest Hills Drive,’ the sneaker makes use of a yellow mesh upper with reinforced overlays in matching yellow and black. J. Cole’s signature Dreamer emblem adorns the back heel. The mid-top rides on a solid black ProFoam midsole with RS foam heel cushioning for improved energy return.

Little Posite One GS 'Volt'
results.story: Made for big kids, the Nike Little Posite One GS ‘Volt’ replicates the look of an eye-catching Air Foamposite Pro colorway originally released in 2014. Nike’s signature fluorescent hue floods the sneaker’s upper, formed with liquid polyurethane poured into a custom mold. A tonal jewel Swoosh adorns lateral side panel, while a contrasting black Swoosh is embroidered on the heel tab. Underfoot, the translucent outsole is equipped with herringbone traction pods for superior grip.

LeBron Witness 5 GS 'Grinch'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike LeBron Witness 5 GS ‘Grinch’ earns its unofficial moniker with a distinctive palette that evokes the iconic Dr. Seuss character. A vibrant Lime Glow hue is applied to the mesh and synthetic upper, featuring interior cables looped into the lacing system for midfoot lockdown. Bright Mango accents land on the webbing pull tab, molded heel clip and visible Zoom Air units nestled under the forefoot of the soft foam midsole. The translucent green outsole is stamped with the initials of LeBron James’ three kids and ‘SFG,’ short for ‘strive for greatness.’

results.name: LeBron Witness 5 GS 'Black Metallic Silver'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike LeBron Witness 5 GS ‘Black Metallic Silver’ combines a lightweight build with game-ready cushioning. The breathable black mesh upper is fortified with tonal synthetic overlays and an integrated lacing system for midfoot lockdown. LeBron James’ initials are embroidered on the pull tab atop the tongue, while his lion logo is debossed on the medial heel. The sneaker rides on a speckled Phylon midsole with a visible Zoom Air unit in the forefoot.

results.name: Flex J 'Black White'
results.story: Made for big kids, the adidas Flex J ‘Black White’ presents a rudimentary colorway of a versatile sneaker built for everyday wear. The black textile upper is equipped with bootie-style construction and multiple rows of eyelets that allow for a custom fit. Underfoot, an Ortholite sockliner works in concert with a lightweight EVA sole unit to deliver cushioned comfort. Flex grooves provide both enhanced traction and freedom of movement.

results.name: Sunray Adjust 5 V2 GS 'Blue Void'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Sunray Adjust 5 V2 GS ‘Blue Void’ showcases aqueous hues on a warm-weather sandal that can be worn in or out of the water. Quick-drying synthetic is used on the ventilated upper, featuring a secure fit via adjustable hook-and-loop straps that wrap over the midfoot and around the heel. The slip-on is mounted on a soft foam sole unit, featuring flex grooves underfoot for enhanced traction and freedom of movement.

results.name: Flex J 'White Glow Blue'
results.story: Constructed for big kids, the adidas Flex J ‘White Glow Blue’ places a premium on comfort, featuring a sock-like textile upper with multiple rows of eyelets for custom lacing and a personalized fit. Contrasting pops of blue and orange make their way to synthetic overlays that fortify the lightweight, seamless build. The sneaker is mounted on a soft foam sole unit enhanced with a series of flex grooves underfoot, offering improved traction combined with a flexible ride.

results.name: Air Max Axis GS 'Laser Blue Chile Red'
results.story: Developed for big kids, the Nike Air Max Axis GS ‘Laser Blue Chile Red’ takes its design cues from the brand’s late ‘90s running shoes. A looped lacing system secures the black mesh upper, reinforced with a wavy fused overlay that recalls the Air Max 98. The lightweight build is mounted on a full-length foam midsole, enhanced with a visible Max Air unit in the heel. Underfoot, the two-tone outsole features a modified waffle tread in a further nod to the 98.

results.name: Adilette Sandals J 'Clear Pink'
results.story: Designed for big kids, the adidas Adilette Sandals J ‘Clear Pink’ showcases pastel hues on a cushioned sandal made for warm-weather wear. The upper features a wide forefoot strap marked with debossed adidas branding, along with a hook-and-loop heel strap that offers a custom fit. The Cloudfoam midsole is topped with a contoured footbed for step-in comfort. Underfoot, the outsole uses a classic herringbone tread for optimal grip.

results.name: Ultra 4.2 TT Jr 'Black Yellow Alert'
results.story: An indoor soccer shoe made for big kids, the PUMA Ultra 4.2 TT Jr ‘Black Yellow Alert’ carries a low-profile upper constructed from lightweight polyurethane. The seamless surface is covered in a dynamic multicolor print exhibited throughout PUMA’s Ultra lineup, featuring an embossed texture for improved touch. The lightweight build is mounted on a non-marking rubber outsole, equipped with a multidirectional traction pattern specifically designed for flat, indoor surfaces.

results.name: Future Z 4.1 IT Jr 'Yellow Alert'
results.story: The PUMA Future Z 4.1 IT Jr ‘Yellow Alert’ showcases an eye-catching two-tone color scheme on an indoor soccer shoe built for big kids. Lightweight and durable polyurethane is utilized on the upper, featuring embossed details in key strike zones for enhanced ball control. A knit collar provides a full range of motion, while an integrated heel counter delivers rearfoot stability. Multidirectional traction arrives via an asymmetric Dynamic Motion System outsole.

results.name: Gel Resolution 8 GS 'Mako Blue'
results.story: A performance tennis shoe made for grade schoolers, the ASICS Gel Resolution 8 GS ‘Mako Blue’ utilizes a proprietary Flexion Fit upper that wraps the foot in snug, form-fitting comfort. A torque control heel counter offers improved containment during quick transitions, while the foam midsole integrates Dynawall technology for midfoot stability during lateral movements. Gel cushioning in the heel delivers enhanced shock absorption. Underfoot, the AHAR outsole — an acronym for ASICS High Abrasion Rubber — provides exceptionally durable traction.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Low GS 'Ditsy Floral'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Low GS ‘Ditsy Floral’ makes use of a black canvas upper bursting with blue and pink florals. The latter hue is repeated on Converse branding hits at the tongue and heel, as well as the dual pinstripes that accent the white rubber midsole. A SmartFOAM sockliner provides lightweight comfort, while the brown rubber outsole features the Chuck Taylor’s signature diamond-shaped traction pattern.

results.name: Sunray Protect 2 PS 'Purple Nebula'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Sunray Protect 2 PS ‘Purple Nebula’ showcases candy-bright hues on a cushioned sandal made for warm-weather adventures. Quick-drying synthetic leather is used on the two-piece upper, featuring a pull tab on the tongue and dual hook-and-loop closure for a personalized fit. A contoured footbed combines with a plush foam midsole to deliver a comfortable ride, while the rubber outsole is treated to a wavy traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Ultra 2.2 FG/AG Jr 'Speed of Light'
results.story: The PUMA Ultra 2.2 FG/AG Jr ‘Speed of Light’ delivers a vibrant colorway of a firm-ground soccer cleat made for big kids. The lightweight MATRYXEVO upper, constructed from a blend of Aramid fiber and Carbon yarn, features a GripControl Pro coating for enhanced ball control. Underfoot, the TPU SpeedUnit outsole uses a studded configuration inspired by PUMA’s track spikes, allowing for both explosive acceleration and abrupt changes of direction.

results.name: Air Max Axis GS 'Blue Void Black'
Sunray Protect 2 PS 'Fireberry'
results.story: The Nike Sunray Protect 2 PS 'Fireberry' features soft cushioning on a versatile warm-weather sandal made for little kids. A vibrant magenta hue is applied to the quick-drying synthetic leather upper, featuring a closed toe, ventilated perforations and dual hook-and-loop closure for a custom fit. A plush foam midsole is supported underfoot by a durable rubber outsole, complete with a wavy traction pattern that offers reliable grip on wet or dry surfaces.

Ultra 4.2 IT Jr 'Black Yellow Alert'
results.story: An indoor soccer shoe made for big kids, the PUMA Ultra 4.2 IT Jr ‘Black Yellow Alert’ features a lightweight, minimalist build designed with speed and agility in mind. A thin tongue and padded collar enhance the fit of the one-piece polyurethane upper, finished with embossed detailing for improved support and control. The low boot silhouette is mounted on a non-marking rubber outsole, its traction pattern specifically configured to handle flat indoor surfaces.

results.name: Air Max Excee GS 'Power Up'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Air Max Excee GS ‘Power Up’ highlights vibrant accents on a casual sneaker that takes its design cues from the iconic Air Max 90. The pops of color include a transparent neon green Swoosh and teal heel patch, both of which stand out against a mesh and leather upper in neutral grey and black tones. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a full-length foam midsole, featuring a TPU plate that frames the neon-tinged Max Air unit under the heel.

results.name: Future Z 2.1 FG AG Jr 'Yellow Alert'
results.story: The PUMA Future Z 2.1 FG AG Jr ‘Yellow Alert’ showcases a fluorescent finish on a performance soccer cleat made for big kids. The flexible knit upper is treated to a GripControl Pro coating for enhanced ball control in key strike zones. An elastic FUZIONFIT+ compression band delivers midfoot lockdown, while an integrated heel counter provides added stability. Underfoot, the Dynamic Motion System outsole features an agility-focused stud configuration made for firm natural surfaces and artificial turf.

results.name: Future Z 4.1 TT Jr 'Yellow Alert'
results.story: The PUMA Future Z 4.1 TT Jr ‘Yellow Alert’ presents a big kids’ soccer cleat made for play on natural grass and artificial turf. A fluorescent finish is applied to the one-piece polyurethane upper, featuring a flexible knit collar and integrated heel counter for enhanced stability. Embossed detailing is applied to key strike zones for improved touch and control. Underfoot, the Dynamic Motion System outsole is equipped with a strategic rubber stud configuration for multidirectional traction.
